---
title: Italian Pepper Steak Sandos with Melty Mozzarella & Roasted Potato Wedges
description: What’s not to love about the classic hoagie (or sub, or grinder, or wedge) filled with savory steak, lightly charred veggies, and melty cheese? We’ll wait. In the meantime, our homage to the classic sando boasts saucy diced steak, a blanket of melty mozz, sautéed onion and bell pepper, and garlic mayo all stuffed inside garlic-butter-brushed baguettes. One bite will have you head over heels.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/italian-pepper-steak-sandos-5e0bc2c6.jpg
